This roadmap is designed to cover the Databricks skills commonly expected for **10–15 LPA Data Engineer** roles with around **1–2 years of experience**.

We'll study **one topic at a time**. For every topic, we'll cover:

* Concept and theory
* Architecture
* Syntax (where applicable)
* Real-world use cases
* Advantages and limitations
* Interview questions
* Hands-on exercise
* Mini assignment

Only after you're comfortable with that topic will we move to the next one.
